snippet.title: Version 1.1 Teaser - "Undercover R&B" | Zenless Zone Zero
snippet.description:
How do you define evil and good?
"Lotus flowers bloom from mud, yet emerge spotless, cleansed in the flowing water, yet don't appear overly alluring."
That's the way it is. Some forms of beauty can only be admired from afar and must not be toyed with. Otherwise...

—Welcome to New Eridu!—
HoYoverse's all-new urban fantasy ARPG, Zenless Zone Zero, is out now on PS5, iOS, Android, and PC: https://hoyo.link/5DbjFDAL.
Log in for 30 free pulls.
Complete the relevant events to obtain at most free pull ×100, Boopon ×80, as well as other in-game rewards such as A-Rank Agents, etc.
